# Dependencias
**/node_modules/**

# Builds y artefactos compilados
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.angular/**
lambda_code/**/dist/
lambda_code/**/*.zip

# Nx cache y temporales
**/.nx/**
**/tmp/**
**/out-tsc/**

# Terraform (providers, state, zips bootstrap)
**/.terraform/**
**/.artifacts/**
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example

# Lockfiles grandes (no aportan al contexto de código)
package-lock.json

# IDE / OS
**/.idea/**
**/.vscode/**
**/.DS_Store

# Logs y coverage
**/*.log
**/coverage/**

# Binarios y mapas de source (solo ruido para el índice)
**/*.map
**/*.js.map
